  2,16,"Àwọn wọ̀nyẹn ni àwọn tí wọ́n fi ìmọ̀nà ra ìṣìnà.Nítorí náà, òkòwò wọn kò lérè, wọn kò sì jẹ́ olùmọ̀nà. {1}",footnotes:1:Ọmọ ‘Abbās - kí Allāhu yọ́nú sí àwọn méjèèjì - sọ pé, “Wọ́n mú ìṣìnà, wọ́n sì fi ìmọ̀nà sílẹ̀.” Tafsīr bun Kathīr. Ọmọ ‘Abbās - kí Allāhu yọ́nú sí àwọn méjèèjì - sọ pé, “Wọ́n mú ìṣìnà, wọ́n sì fi ìmọ̀nà sílẹ̀.” Tafsīr bun Kathīr.
